OL,3,CBrewer says increased alcohol duty
OL,4,Cwill threaten struggling industry
OL,6,FAn increase in alcohol duty will put
OL,7,Feven more pressure on small businesses
OL,8,Ftrying to survive in an already-
OL,9,Fdifficult industry, according to an
OL,10,FOxfordshire brewer.
OL,12,FJim Southey set up the LoveBeer
OL,13,FBrewery, at Milton, near Abingdon, 10
OL,14,Fyears ago. It's a family business
OL,15,Fwhich has seen steady growth.
