OL,3,CBrewer says increased alcohol duty
OL,4,Cwill threaten struggling industry
OL,6,FBut he's worried a hike in alcohol
OL,7,Fduty at the beginning of February
OL,8,Fcould threaten the future of the
OL,9,Fcompany. "We've cut all our costs as
OL,10,Fmuch as we can - we have solar panels,
OL,11,Fwe recycle - but it's a tough
OL,12,Fbusiness," he said.
OL,14,FHe added: "The increased pressure of
OL,15,Fcosts just makes that even harder to
OL,16,Fgive these guys a living in what is a
OL,17,Fvery traditional business that we're
OL,18,Ftrying to continue."
