OL,3,CBrewer says increased alcohol duty
OL,4,Cwill threaten struggling industry
OL,6,FIn the November budget the Chancellor
OL,7,FRachel Reeves confirmed that all
OL,8,Falcohol duty rates will increase by
OL,9,F3.66% in line with inflation.
OL,11,FDespite funding the business' capital
OL,12,Fcosts himself and growing its turnover
OL,13,Fto #100,000 a year, Jim is concerned
OL,14,Fwhat rising duties will mean for his
OL,15,Fstaff in what he described as a 'very
OL,16,Fmarginal business'.
OL,18,F"We employ two people here, we've
OL,19,Fgrown the business from scratch," he
OL,20,Fsaid. "I started it myself, I've put
OL,21,Fin all the capital myself."
