OL,3,CBrewer says increased alcohol duty
OL,4,Cwill threaten struggling industry
OL,6,FAt LoveBeer they brew traditional cask
OL,7,Fale and sell to the public and to
OL,8,Fpubs. Their beers are named after dogs
OL,9,Fbelonging to family and friends.
OL,11,FThe brewery also holds its own
OL,12,Ffestivals and sells in farm shops and
OL,13,Fonline. It has a great deal of
OL,14,Fcommunity support but with cost
OL,15,Fincreases on the way, it's doing
OL,16,Feverything possible to keep the
OL,17,Fbusiness thriving.
