OL,3,CBrewer says increased alcohol duty
OL,4,Cwill threaten struggling industry
OL,6,FHarry Benbow, a brewer and Director,
OL,7,Fsaid an increase in duty of just over
OL,8,Fthree and a half percent, is not a
OL,9,Fcost they can pass on easily.
OL,11,FHarry said: "Most pubs just cannot
OL,12,Ftake any more increase on the price we
OL,13,Fcharge them. They make very little
OL,14,Fmoney on cask ale anyway. It's got a
OL,15,Fshelf life that kegged beer, wine and
OL,16,Fspirits don't.
OL,18,F"It only lasts a week once it's open.
