OL,3,CBrewer says increased alcohol duty
OL,4,Cwill threaten struggling industry
OL,6,F"It's going to have less of an
OL,7,Fincentive to grow if you're going to
OL,8,Fbe worried about the tax burden in the
OL,9,Ffuture, so if the Government wants
OL,10,Feconomic growth, they need to be
OL,11,Fhaving policies in place that support
OL,12,Fsmall business rather than stifle it."
OL,14,FHe said his party would like to see a
OL,15,F5% VAT cut for hospitality and pubs.
OL,17,FA spokesman for HM Treasury said that
OL,18,Fmaintaining alcohol duty rates in line
OL,19,Fwith inflation is fiscally responsible.
