OL,3,CBrewer says increased alcohol duty
OL,4,Cwill threaten struggling industry
OL,6,FThey said: "Our breweries are vital to
OL,7,FBritain's economy, so we're making it
OL,8,Feasier for them to thrive: no export
OL,9,Fduty, lower licensing fees, reduced
OL,10,Ftariffs, and a cap on corporation tax.
OL,12,F"While our Small Business Plan is
OL,13,Fbacking UK pub and brewery owners with
OL,14,Ftailored support alongside new plans
OL,15,Fto slash red tape, speed up licensing
OL,16,Freforms and create fairer business
OL,17,Frates with our #4.3bn support package."
